* The expand/collapse buttons of the `toc` macros now carry `aria-label`s, so screen readers announce them instead of an empty button (fixes [[Issue #9794|https://github.com/TiddlyWiki/TiddlyWiki5/issues/9794]])
* TOC entries are wrapped in a `tc-toc-item-row` flex row; custom CSS that targets `.toc-item > a` for layout may need updating to the new class
